Module org.opengis.geoapi.example

Package org.opengis.example

package org.opengis.example
Access to examples of GeoAPI implementations. This package is provided only for illustrative purposes with simple implementations. This package is not for use in production. For real applications, use a library implementing GeoAPI or providing GeoAPI wrappers.
